703950f-a.title: Brooklyn: Degraw Street - Hicks Street
703950f-a.text:
Degraw Street, north side, from L.icks Street to Miffany Place, shown in a sey of two views. In the center of the block is the Roman Catholic Church of the Sacred Heart of Jesus and Mary.
To its left is the H. Behr plant.
P. L. perr  January 10, 1941
NO REPRODUCTIONS  Views 1,2
